{"tid":2379454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中印衝突｜中方部隊越境爆毆鬥 解放軍20人傷 印度4傷","createTime":"2021-01-25T08:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T11:24:53.000Z","uid":227801,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"d5fb7de5b54d12b66ff5c2c141f232a4b2722d60","tid":2379454,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:48:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210125/DBHUUDU4GVDXFL6V6AUVEEXKNM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210125%2FDBHUUDU4GVDXFL6V6AUVEEXKNM%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=d3f7a979\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210125%2FDBHUUDU4GVDXFL6V6AUVEEXKNM%2F&h=4203f28e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210125/DBHUUDU4GVDXFL6V6AUVEEXKNM/</a><br />\n中國與印度進行第9輪軍事磋商之際，兩國邊境再次出現衝突。印度傳媒表示錫金邦北部的納庫拉（Naku La）地區日前有中國士兵越境，雙方爆發衝突，各有士兵受傷，其中中國解放軍最少20名士兵受傷，印度則有4人受傷，目前衝突已結束，但氣氛仍然緊張。<br />\n<br />\n印媒指衝突在3天前發生，消息人士稱中國部隊試圖跨越錫金附近的邊境，遭印方士兵截停，雙方其後毆鬥，但據報沒人開槍，中方部隊事後亦退回原有控制區。<br />\n<br />\n衝突發生在中印再舉行軍事磋商之際<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n............................................."},{"pid":"6f719b3b32e88757d326538ef864db6bd9eb95c8","tid":2379454,"uid":58630,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:49:33.000Z","msg":"20:4 又贏一仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0b39b62738d9f8bc574c116df2ecfdabebbb19","tid":2379454,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b947b4a37205a36189324715b6fbf3aff41b0ab","tid":2379454,"uid":21545,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:52:49.000Z","msg":"20:4 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同鄕好波"},{"pid":"95f7030854614377ec29c77c0d056ace6611dc00